	<div class='heading'>
		<%= session['brand'] %> is a place that makes book clubs more fun.
	</div>
	<ul class='about'>
		<li>
			<div>📖</div><p>Quickly find and add your club's books</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<div>✎</div><p>Write notes and reviews to promote discussion</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<div>⭐</div><p>Add ratings to your club's books</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<div>📈</div><p>Keep track of statistics, such as whose books get the highest ratings</p>
